    .text-title-home-page.w-75.mx-auto
      | Embracing an uncluttered, laid-back luxury concept, the brand new 5-star Astra Hotel Resort will enchant you with its minimally sumptuous interiors—a brilliant blend of modern luxury aesthetics with the all-time classic Cycladic architecture. Gracefully lying a breath away from the gorgeous black-sanded beach of Kamari, the stately hotel boasts a privileged location among the restaurants, bars and social happenings of Kamari, offering at the same time, tranquil surroundings to unwind in privacy.
      br
      br
      | The Astra Hotel Resort signature luxury rooms and suites are all about supreme comfort in a sophisticated ambiance, topped off with indulging amenities to make you feel pampered. Designed for discerning travelers who appreciate refined luxury, the rooms and suites follow a traditional Cycladic outline with arches, smooth lines and cotton-white walls embellished with an exotic boho-chic décor and high-end furnishings.
      br
      br
      | Discover the gastronomic treasure that is hidden in the famous Astra restaurant, which is operating exclusively within Astra Resort! Α luxurious, contemporary bar-restaurant with fine, unique flavors that will seduce your palate awaits you, from the very heart of Italy. Delectable dishes prepared by professional chefs, maestros of authentic Italian cuisine, and invigorating drinks will frame your dinners against the backdrop of the spectacular views of Santorini.
